  <summary>4/10/1997--Introduced.
Amends the Safe Drinking Water Act to allow public water systems supplied by surface water sources, after a 12-month period in which a State determines which systems must adopt water filtration standards, to apply to a State agency for a determination that such system is not required to use filtration.</summary>
